	 <title>System.Duration</title> 
	 <para></para> 
	 <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Remarks</bridgehead> 
	 <para>This is a TimeSpan operator that returns a positive TimeSpan value
		  for the specified value. It is equivalent to the Absolute value
		  (<symbol>System.Abs</symbol>) operator for number type values. </para> 
	 <example> 
		  <title>Example</title> 
		  <programlisting>select TableDee add { Duration(-TimeSpan.Ticks(10000000)) Duration };</programlisting> 
		  <programlisting>Duration
--------
1sec</programlisting> 
	 </example> 
